Dialogue: 1,0:00:29.00,0:00:32.09,chs&eng,,0,0,8,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs20\b1\bord6\fsp4\c&H6FBADF&\3c&HD77742&}全民警察
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.45,0:01:08.11,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接著來 哥們\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Take it, brother.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.16,0:01:58.78,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}打倒你!\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Let me break you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.75,0:02:04.21,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗨 這真可怕!\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Man, that was funky.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.72,0:03:09.14,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 前面注意! - 噢 我猜會議已經開始了\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Fore! - Well, I guess the meeting's started.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.73,0:03:14.52,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 您好 長官! - 馬霍尼! 瓊斯!\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Howdy, sir? - Mahoney! Jones!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.98,0:03:16.86,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝 斯威特查克\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Thank you, Sweetchuck.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.40,0:03:21.03,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}關於我的新計劃我得到了極棒極棒的消息\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I've had the most wonderful newsabout my new program.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.70,0:03:30.12,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 長官 是什麼新計劃? - 全市公民作為警察巡邏計劃\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- What new program is that, sir? - My citizens on patrol.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.25,0:03:32.25,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}簡單點 我叫它"全民警察"\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I call it C.O.P. for short.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.29,0:03:34.58,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不錯的警察團體 你們說呢?\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Has a nice policey ring to it,don't you think?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:36.29,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼是"全民警察" 長官?\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What is C.O.P., sir?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.13,0:03:41.88,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}警察工作最讓人感到灰心喪氣的是什麼?\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What is the most frustrating thingabout police work?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.01,0:03:45.68,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 不給配備手榴彈 - 隔離室 長官\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Not being able to carry hand grenades. - Separate locker rooms, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.76,0:03:47.56,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}令人作嘔的藍制服\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Icky blue uniforms.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.89,0:03:50.68,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一直認為最讓人洩氣的事情是…\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I always thoughtthat the most frustrating thing was that...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.77,0:03:53.73,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們不能立刻趕到所有的犯罪現場去解決所有的犯罪\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}we couldn't be everywhere at onceto solve every crime.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.77,0:03:56.90,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以最終公眾會把我們當作敵人\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So the public ends upthinking of us as enemies.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.44,0:04:00.69,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果他們能把我們所有人都看作朋友該有多好啊!\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Wouldn't it be wonderfulif we could all be friends?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.86,0:04:04.20,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊 馬霍尼警官 請進來\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Officer Mahoney, please come in.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.99,0:04:07.57,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來點檸檬水 我喜歡喝檸檬水\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Have some lemonade. I love lemonade.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.99,0:04:12.33,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 別太酸了 別… - …太甜了 嗯 不錯\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Not too tart, not - - - Too sweet, just good.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.75,0:04:20.21,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以"全民警察"是一項社會行動計劃 長官\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So C.O.P. isa community action program, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:24.59,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 就像鄰里監督組織? - 更強! 更棒!\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Like Neighborhood Watch? - More. Much more!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.30,0:04:27.34,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們向公眾顯示我們的關心\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We show the community that we care.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.47,0:04:32.18,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們訓練志願者們如何進行犯罪偵查如何進行急救 還有、還有…\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We train volunteers in crime detection,in first - aid and....{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.60,0:04:36.23,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 還有這是個不錯的主意 長官 - 但我們需要公眾的支持\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- And it's a great idea, sir. - But we need citizen support.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.90,0:04:39.61,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}周邊的犯罪活動會讓您得到他們的支持的\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}With all this neighborhood crime,I'm sure you'll get it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.65,0:04:42.06,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 前面注意! - 沒錯 如果我們…\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Fore! - Right. What if we were to....{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.53,0:04:44.78,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果什麼?\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What was that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.70,0:04:48.03,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我相信斯威特查克兄弟想建議…\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I believe brother Sweetchuckis suggesting...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.11,0:04:50.24,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們在我們附近招募新兵\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}we recruit in our old neighborhood.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.33,0:04:53.41,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好主意! 我們有市長的全力支持…\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Excellent. We have the full supportof the Mayor...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.54,0:04:57.71,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最棒的是 州長希望我下月…\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and best of all, the Governor of the statewants me to unveil the program...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.71,0:05:01.25,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在英國舉行的國際警察大會的最後…\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}at the end ofthe International Police Seminar...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.38,0:05:02.96,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把這一計劃公諸於眾\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}next month in England.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.67,0:05:05.67,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在我參會的時候…\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}While I attend the seminar...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.71,0:05:08.80,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們 我的好朋友們…\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you, my good friends...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.84,0:05:10.97,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}將把"全民警察"計劃付諸實施\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}will put C.O.P. into action.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.26,0:05:14.68,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這將改善全世界的警民關係\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It will change community relationsall around the world.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.14,0:05:18.02,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拉薩方法\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The Lassard Method.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.64,0:05:22.40,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聽起來不錯 是吧?\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It rolls nicely off the tongue,don't you think?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.82,0:05:24.52,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗨 我錯過了什麼?\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Hi! What did I miss?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.86,0:05:31.95,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗨\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Hi.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.59,0:05:48.42,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哈里斯上尉 赫斯特委員來了\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Capt. Harris,Police Commissioner Hurst is here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.46,0:05:49.67,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}您想見他嗎?\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You want to see him?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.72,0:05:51.55,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 把他趕走\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No. Send him packing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.01,0:05:54.01,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是 長官!\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yes, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.14,0:05:56.60,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 學監! - 什麼事 長官?\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Proctor! - Yes, sir?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.72,0:05:59.31,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}立即把他請進來\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Send the Commissioner in immediately.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.43,0:06:02.68,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 我想您說要把他趕走 - 馬上!\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- I thought you said to send him packing. - Immediately!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.77,0:06:04.02,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是 長官!\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yes, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.35,0:06:06.98,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒用的東西\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Nincompoop.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.73,0:06:10.15,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}委員\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Commissioner.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.57,0:06:14.65,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 你有問題 哈里斯上尉? - 是的 長官\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- You have a problem, Capt. Harris? - Yes, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.74,0:06:19.58,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}委員先生 我對這張從拉薩那裏來的傳單非常關心…\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Commissioner, I am extremely concernedwith this memorandum from Lassard...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.66,0:06:22.37,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}關於他的"全民警察"計劃\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}about his C.O.P. program.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.33,0:06:27.04,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}讓市民去做警察工作? 多蠢的想法\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Citizens doing police work?An asinine idea.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.38,0:06:32.21,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果這被通過 警察的工作、薪水都將沒有保證\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If this goes through, no policeman's job,no policeman's paycheck, will be safe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.30,0:06:33.88,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是不是不想幹了?\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Are you through, Captain?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.88,0:06:38.51,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}州長認為這個計劃非常的有創意\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The Governor of this state thinksthat this program is absolutely brilliant.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.31,0:06:43.47,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果他改變主意我就會同意你的看法\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So until he changes his mind,that's what you and I think, too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.89,0:06:45.02,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒意見吧?\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Agreed?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.35,0:06:47.23,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 沒有 長官 - 很好\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Yes, sir. - Good.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.53,0:06:56.65,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}您一開始很英明您真應該把他趕走\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You were right.You should have sent him packing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.78,0:07:00.11,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我才不在乎州長跟市長會怎麼想\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I don't give a damnwhat the Governor or the Mayor thinks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.24,0:07:03.53,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拉薩的計劃是個錯誤…\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Lassard's program is a mistake...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.37,0:07:07.41,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}任何同意他的想法都是錯的\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and anyone who thinks otherwiseis wrong.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.08,0:07:10.67,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}完全錯誤\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Pure and simple.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.80,0:07:13.38,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別碰它!\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Don't touch those!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.92,0:07:16.92,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我看你再敢不經我允許就碰我的球!\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Don't you ever touch my ballswithout asking!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.27,0:07:37.03,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請你離開這我會報警! 我是認真的\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You're gonna have to leave.I'll call the police. I mean it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.11,0:07:40.40,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}行、行 我這就走 離開這\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Okay, I'm going. I'm out of here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.53,0:07:44.11,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等會兒 我就是警察\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Wait a minute. I am the police.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:49.25,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 不 你不是 - 我是 我來這想談一下"全民警察"計劃\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- No, you're not. - That's me. I'm here to speak about C.O.P.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.33,0:07:55.04,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉 我沒有…沒有警服…\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'm sorry. I didn't....Without the uniform on - -{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.17,0:07:58.59,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}便裝會使公民感覺更舒服\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Regular human clothesmake people more comfortable.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.17,0:08:04.14,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗨 女士們 我們來作詩吧!\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Hi, ladies. Let's do some poetry!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.31,0:08:15.02,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我今晚得去丈人家吃晚飯\N{\fncronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I got to go to my in - laws'for dinner tonight.{\r}
